Dialogue: 1,0:22:50.26,0:22:55.81,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur1\bord0}Eu sempre acreditei que nos encontraríamos novamente desde aquele dia
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.85,0:23:01.19,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur1\bord0}Se tivermos coração, seremos reunidos de novo
Dialogue: 1,0:23:01.23,0:23:11.58,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur1\bord0}Desperte a energia infinita
Dialogue: 1,0:23:11.62,0:23:17.21,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur1\bord0}Antes que você se machuque
Dialogue: 1,0:23:17.25,0:23:23.30,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur1\bord0}Encontre o que você pode fazer... Por favor
Dialogue: 1,0:23:23.34,0:23:28.47,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur1\bord0}Não jogue fora por causa desta idade dolorosa
Dialogue: 1,0:23:29.18,0:23:31.81,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur1\bord0}Até o dia em que olharmos novamente
Dialogue: 1,0:23:31.81,0:23:38.81,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur1\bord0}para o céu azul que um dia vimos.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:14.91,0:00:22.09,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,100)\blur1\bord0}Beijando suavemente a estrela de água que dorme em azul,
Dialogue: 1,0:00:22.09,0:00:30.84,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1\bord0}Uma pessoa que acende o fogo da vida,
Dialogue: 1,0:00:30.84,0:00:35.72,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1\bord0}O tempo, a ondulação dourada,
Dialogue: 1,0:00:35.72,0:00:44.48,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1\bord0}é um suspiro dos lábios do céu,
Dialogue: 1,0:00:44.48,0:00:48.74,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1\bord0}As estrelas da bondade...
Dialogue: 1,0:00:48.74,0:00:51.70,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1\bord0}...enterradas no coração acendem...
Dialogue: 1,0:00:51.70,0:00:55.87,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1\bord0}...e chamam umas às outras,
Dialogue: 1,0:00:55.87,0:01:02.83,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,1700)\blur1\bord0}Como navios naufragados vagando nas ondas...
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.83,0:01:08.30,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1\bord0}Não chore mais,
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.30,0:01:15.64,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1\bord0}porque agora tem alguém procurando por
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.64,0:01:20.39,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,700)\blur1\bord0}ansioso para ver
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.26,0:22:55.81,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Eu tenho acreditado que nos encontraremos novamente desde aquele dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.85,0:23:01.19,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Se tivermos coração, nos reuniremos novamente
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.23,0:23:11.58,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Desperte a energia infinita
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.62,0:23:17.21,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Antes que você se machuque
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.25,0:23:23.30,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Encontre o que você pode fazer... Por favor
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.34,0:23:28.47,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}\NDon't throw it away because of this painful age
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.18,0:23:31.81,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Enquanto não olharmos novamente para o céu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.81,0:23:38.81,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}no céu azul que um dia vimos
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.91,0:00:22.09,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,100)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Beijando suavemente a estrela de água que dorme em azul.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:30.84,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Uma pessoa que acende a chama da vida
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.84,0:00:35.72,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}O tempo, a onda dourada
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.72,0:00:44.48,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}é um suspiro dos lábios do céu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.48,0:00:48.74,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Estrelas de bondade...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.74,0:00:51.70,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Enterrado em chamas do coração...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.70,0:00:55.87,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}...e chamam uns aos outros,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.87,0:01:02.83,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,1700)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Como navios naufragados vagueando nas ondas...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:08.30,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Não chore mais
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.30,0:01:15.64,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}porque agora há uma pessoa procurando por você
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.64,0:01:20.39,Song ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,700)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Morrendo de vontade de ver você...
Dialogue: 1,0:22:47.05,0:22:49.39,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\fs68\blur1\bord0}Ah, eu não consigo deixar de acreditar em você
Dialogue: 1,0:22:50.26,0:22:55.81,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur1\bord0}Acreditei até hoje
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.85,0:23:01.19,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur1\bord0}Se eu ainda tiver esperança no meu coração...
Dialogue: 1,0:23:01.23,0:23:11.58,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur1\bord0}Chamando a Energia do Infinito
Dialogue: 1,0:23:11.62,0:23:17.21,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur1\bord0}Estou ferido, Mãe
Dialogue: 1,0:23:17.25,0:23:23.30,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur1\bord0}Vou fazer o que for possível
Dialogue: 1,0:23:23.34,0:23:28.47,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur1\bord0}Quando você estiver sofrendo, é melhor aguentar
Dialogue: 1,0:23:29.18,0:23:31.81,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur1\bord0}Já vi este céu outrora
Dialogue: 1,0:23:31.81,0:23:38.81,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur1\bord0}Até nos encontrarmos novamente
Dialogue: 1,0:00:14.91,0:00:22.09,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,100)\blur1\bord0}Sob as estrelas, o azul do mar dorme em paz
Dialogue: 1,0:00:22.09,0:00:30.84,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1\bord0}Beije e tome o dia da sua vida, você que toma vidas.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:30.84,0:00:35.72,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1\bord0}a enxurrada vermelha do tempo
Dialogue: 1,0:00:35.72,0:00:44.48,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1\bord0}Nasci com uma estrela na boca
Dialogue: 1,0:00:44.48,0:00:48.74,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1\bord0}resonou em meu coração
Dialogue: 1,0:00:48.74,0:00:51.70,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1\bord0}A bondura dos que brilham
Dialogue: 1,0:00:51.70,0:00:55.87,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1\bord0}Estou sentindo que vou explodir
Dialogue: 1,0:00:55.87,0:01:02.83,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,1700)\blur1\bord0}Eu me chamo [nome]
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.83,0:01:08.30,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1\bord0}Não me abandone agora!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.30,0:01:15.64,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1\bord0}Há pessoas que estão procurando por você
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.64,0:01:20.39,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,700)\blur1\bord0}Eu quero te encontrar
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.05,0:22:49.39,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\fs68\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Ah, não consigo deixar de acreditar em você
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.26,0:22:55.81,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Necessariamente acreditava naquele dia ou então
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.85,0:23:01.19,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}se houver um coração a ser chamado
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.23,0:23:11.58,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Estamos chamando a energia do infinito
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.62,0:23:17.21,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Ah, que ferida!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.25,0:23:23.30,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Estou procurando coisas que posso fazer
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.34,0:23:28.47,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Quando estiver sofrendo, por favor, aguente
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.18,0:23:31.81,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Vi esse céu azul antes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.81,0:23:38.81,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}até nos encontrarmos de novo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.91,0:00:22.09,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,100)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}água azul adormecida sob as estrelas
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:30.84,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Aproximem-se, aqueles que seguram o dia de sua morte com um beijo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.84,0:00:35.72,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Chuva de sangue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.72,0:00:44.48,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Nasci com uma voz que vem do céu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.48,0:00:48.74,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}<resonou no meu coração>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.74,0:00:51.70,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}<a bondade das estrelas>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.70,0:00:55.87,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Eu vou queimar você
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.87,0:01:02.83,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,1700)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}bum crac tchan no jeito disso
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:08.30,Song JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2\bord0.5\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HFF&}Não aguento mais! Não chore agora!
